{"tid":209823,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"跪求有急材嘅爸絲入一入黎","createTime":"2017-04-20T13:31:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-20T15:20:10.000Z","uid":47109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e4630ac68a805d36817fbfc66254388b51433f33","tid":209823,"uid":47109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T13:31:13.000Z","msg":"最近，家父誤交損友，被灌輸錯誤價值觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢經常都話最近啲大學生都唔係讀書嘅，成日都唔洗返學。本來我都冇刻意記住，今日食完飯佢特登阻住我返入房條路，講說話比我聽<br />\n<br />\n佢：都唔知你地係咪讀書嘅，成日都唔洗返學，又可以返工，又有時間補習。你睇下人地讀私校嘅人啦！人地讀樹仁大學，上堂遲1分鐘都唔得嫁！你呢？成日都唔洗上堂。<br />\n<br />\n無奈我轉數唔夠快，諗唔到點樣可以秒佢，解決晒呢啲無意義嘅對話。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我好肯定呢個情況會再次出現，希望各位巴絲可以幫下小妹"},{"pid":"2fd14c135036a27c23c5d4cb4e884526f83ec645","tid":209823,"uid":47109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T13:32:21.000Z","msg":"打錯標題<br />\n自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951d56dd613379f2d0617afb10e76e0049254158","tid":209823,"uid":56259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T13:35:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5109632a7c96e18dbefddb1052b4c8432df3ebde","tid":209823,"uid":29130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T13:36:52.000Z","msg":"高質教育係咁"},{"pid":"0bb80fe1b0901f5e3f835a1a6282921384cb4d03","tid":209823,"uid":69130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T13:38:41.000Z","msg":"大學生講自習，仲要人教晒所有野個啲先係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58bbd5fc7314bcd7c7c3ede1cc49cca78e7664fe","tid":209823,"uid":104822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T13:38:45.000Z","msg":"垃圾場出來的 只有垃圾<br />\n一句完"},{"pid":"4f701b124ea823fc2